text: Keith Anderson is an American country music singer. He has made two albums. His Three Chord Country and American Rock & Roll album was #1 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart. ==Discography== ;Studio albums * Three Chord Country and American Rock & Roll (2005) * C'mon!
